But I think, you know, depending -- so if you asked me that question in a month or really at the end of the year, because we hope to get this. We hope to get taxes and then infrastructure. And then Im going to do a very big -- were doing very big trade deals, and were looking forward to that. But we want to do, ideally, this first.
You know, a lot of people said you should have started with taxes or you should have started with infrastructure. Well, infrastructure Ill actually have bipartisan support, and I can use infrastructure to carry other things along. So I dont want to waste it at the beginning, if that makes sense.
