Well have to see. You can call him. But I said, Tim, unless you start building your plants in this country, I wont consider my administration an economic success, OK? And hes called me and he says, you know, theyre going forward, three big, beautiful plants. Youll have to call him. I mean, maybe he wont tell you what he tells me, but I believe he will do that. I really believe it.
