Well, I didnt -- I wouldnt have wanted to. But I see the way they go after us on a witch hunt, you know? The Russian -- the Russian storys all an excuse for the Democrats losing. In fact, if you read the book, "Shattered," they have a whole chapter where they sat the day after the election and they said: Yeah, Russia. It was Russia.
